snippet.title: Delta Force: Urban Warfare (PS1) Gameplay [Part 1]
snippet.description:
This is part 1 of a now unfinished playthrough that I was planning for Delta Force: Urban Warfare on the PS1, My computer is still out of commission. This is just footage I had on an exterior hard drive, so I'm not officially back. I"ve only got two parts to this playthrough, so it's not even remotely finished, and I probably won't finish it for a while until I get my setup up and running again. 

For the time being, I'll have to search the external drive to see what other footage I have on it to upload it as well.

This is played on a PS2 with texture smoothing on, and part 1 mostly contains the cut scenes, and a level 1 playthrough. NOTE: at the electrical box, I always forget how to detonate the charges.
